<item>
            <title>[LU-2639] make lod_sync() more robust</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-2639</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Per inspection in &lt;a href=&quot;http://review.whamcloud.com/4921&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://review.whamcloud.com/4921&lt;/a&gt;, lod_sync() should call dt_sync() on all targets, even if some sub-targets return an error.  Also, it should call dt_sync() on all MDT targets as well as OST targets.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
