&lt;ul class=&quot;alternate&quot; type=&quot;square&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;remove &quot;&lt;tt&gt;break&lt;/tt&gt;&quot; from the &lt;tt&gt;lod_sync()&lt;/tt&gt; loops&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;use &quot;&lt;tt&gt;rc2&lt;/tt&gt;&quot; to save the &lt;tt&gt;dt_sync()&lt;/tt&gt; return&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;save the &lt;b&gt;first&lt;/b&gt; non-zero &lt;tt&gt;rc2&lt;/tt&gt; error code that is hit into &lt;tt&gt;rc&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
